{"type": "article", "id": 13108, "title": "“城市绿洲”盆栽", "description": "", "date": "2015-08-06T06:49:44Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 60, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000245Wh4qEtZRgndK6B0F.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t意大利设计师 Andrea Mangone 推出了一个叫做 “Urbanoasis” 的盆栽系列。我们生活中盆栽很常见，但是制作得这么精致的还是蛮难得。整套产品包括一个花盆，种子，干土肥料，浇水罐，甚至还有铲子，耙子等农作用具。有了这些，我们似乎可以有模有样地在家里开一片小农田了。<a href=\"http://www.andreamangone.com/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以查看详细信息。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140739vq75QoGse81uiFEc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.97037037\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140740rNVGIZ6tpikXMAbd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73703704\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140741Tqv0lyPxJ8WSNcFV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.60092593\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140742mFAYjwZH487coCLk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.57685185\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140742NwS71kdeZAHKXDBE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.59074074\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140743SI7cr9iankyK6U2M.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.60185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140744ECkm1RhdJIun6DSY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56018519\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140744RTDz8NIaeB7Jj4Qf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.48888889\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140744d5AKUi3Q0mPJSpLl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.54814815\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n\n"}